Detailed Description

cvmx_mix::_oring1

MIX_ORING1 = MIX Outbound Ring Register #1

Description: NOTE: To write to the MIX_ORING1 register, a device would issue an IOBST directed at the MIO. To read the MIX_ORING1 register, a device would issue an IOBLD64 directed at the MIO.
